Package org.jivesoftware.smackx.bookmark

Interface Summary
SharedBookmark Interface to indicate if a bookmark is shared across the server.
 

Class Summary
BookmarkedConference Respresents a Conference Room bookmarked on the server using JEP-0048 Bookmark Storage JEP.
BookmarkedURL Respresents one instance of a URL defined using JEP-0048 Bookmark Storage JEP.
BookmarkManager Provides methods to manage bookmarks in accordance with JEP-0048.
Bookmarks Bookmarks is used for storing and retrieving URLS and Conference rooms.
Bookmarks.Provider The IQ Provider for BookmarkStorage.
